CustomField.description: This is a Hidden checkbox field for if Constituency does not include EDF Alumni or Staff. This Field is used in an SDG filter - SDG Task Related Contact - Other
CustomField.formula: IF(OR( INCLUDES( Organization_Constituency__c , "EDF Alumni"),INCLUDES( Organization_Constituency__c , "EDF Staff")),False,True)
CustomField.label: Constituency - Other for SGD
